channel.description:
[size=18pt][b]POST OR I WILL REMOVE[/b][/size] Haters gonna hate. I would have kept hosting this but school started again so I have no time to run a server.
[IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/99p4xc.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/15k28h.png[/img] [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/2n1g6df.png[/img] [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/10s4vt5.png[/img] [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/30253ex.png[/img] [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/vni79t.png[/img] [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/2jai9ky.png[/img] [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/2s8semc.png[/img] [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/2h334g8.png[/img] [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/23wsk6d.png[/img] [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/wk5ls4.png[/img] [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/2v2y7ol.png[/img] [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/2dl5ijr.png[/img] [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/6z822h.png[/img] [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/2iji8tl.png[/img] [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/vfz2gx.png[/img] [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/21emus.png[/img] [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/w8xffq.png[/img]
[size=24pt][b]Features:[/b][/size] All combat skills can be trained Thieving Summoning Shops (Decent eco, there is home with lots of shops to buy gear from + donator shop at the donator zone) Donator System Lots of bosses Trading (still not 100% but better than most dementhium servers) Clan Chat Safe Pking Warriors Guild Clan wars! AND LOT'S MORE
PS - LAG FIXES WERE NOT RELEASED WITH THIS AS THEY WERE NOT MINE TO RELEASE -
Server: http://bit.ly/orsQsB aka http://uppit.com/uxdfy1ovrgl2/google_634_-_marcbob_was_here.rar Client: http://bit.ly/ouXSsj aka http://uppit.com/rmh5731ew94t/google_634_client.rar Cache: http://uppit.com/exwcvc7jt1uz/cache.rar
[b]READ THIS:[/b] In order to get the server to work, you must extract the cache in two locations which I will tell you (BOTH SERVER SIDE AND CLIENT SIDE). Why didn't I just leave the cache in the server and client? The files would be big as hell then. Server Side Directions: Make a folder in rune|mtp634/data/cache (without the |, it censors the name without the |)(you will have to make the folder "cache" and then extract the cache files into it Client Side Directions: Look for the folder called .dementhium_cache_32 and extract the cache in there.
I'll say a couple more very basic things, but honestly if you can't figure this stuff out then you shouldn't be running a server.
To change the [b]client ip[/b], go to launch.java and search for 0.0.0.0 (there are two locations with 0.0.0.0 being set as the ip and you must change both.
How do I make admins and mods? In the server files, go to rune mtp/src/org/dementhium/net/ and open ActionSender.java and look for public static final String[] ADMINS = { "Marc", "Marcbob"}; + public static final String[] MODERATORS = {"Josh", "ipk_mods", "Nick"};
Replace the usernames with the ones you want as admin and mod, compile, and run the server.
[b]Credits: [/b] Me Random Tutorials I found that explained random shit Tyluur Canownueasy Mystic Flow (dementhium base)
This be like me 15th release all time dawg
